{"tid":1390313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重想跪到幾時？","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:20:05.000Z","uid":50719,"like":22,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"418c54ecff378f5e663634b9ad799d61768149c0","tid":1390313,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmCQ7SL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmCQ7SL.png&h=7b99bc14&s={SIZE}\" />又跪，一日到黑都跪，咁多野可以做，咁多人等住你幫，你走去跪，香港人幾時先會明跪，賣慘，賣悲情係無用？<br />\n<br />\n你去道歉，去接力絕食都好過你跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你要賣慘就去前線跪係d路障前面，順便幫手擋下布袋彈"},{"pid":"f9fb55f72275cd59e74a2cbf1d4b77a01628d54b","tid":1390313,"uid":261505,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:16:24.000Z","msg":"分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f533ca7e7294c137e12888ad978433288c710ac6","tid":1390313,"uid":59297,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:16:35.000Z","msg":"咁又要屌？<br />\n<br />\n就係班香港人受軟唔受硬先要用呢招<br />\n<br />\n你又知冇上過前線擋彈？"},{"pid":"30c3e4bd0288529fdf12499ba74f75695367c39a","tid":1390313,"uid":85574,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"我覺得兩睇，那怕係影響一個廢中，都已經好好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係人人都ready上前線支持，如果我地重割呢樣割嗰樣，好快好似日本當年反安保咁"},{"pid":"058ed1554eaa4236f38ed7347361e035477dc201","tid":1390313,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"香港人受軟唔受硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b755df4e09f45516a6369dee17b093a34d925c4","tid":1390313,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"大陸維權人仕，最鍾意下跪。"},{"pid":"7087bb4e470e7b5e94289359298576ae6ae91d0b","tid":1390313,"uid":290355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"